# Created      : 12 May 2021
# Updated      : 05 Oct 2025
# Comments     : Backup of Cinnamon keybindings stored in ~/.config
#              : Tested with Cinnamon DE on Mint 19.x & 20.x, 21.x, 22.x, LMDE 5/6, Debian 10/11/12
